Auth (Public):
POST /api/v1/auth/register
POST /api/v1/auth/login
POST /api/v1/auth/logout

Users (Authenticated):
GET /api/v1/users/me
GET /api/v1/users/search?q=username

Conversations (Authenticated):
GET /api/v1/conversations - List with last message
POST /api/v1/conversations/direct - Get or create direct chat
GET /api/v1/conversations/:id/messages - Get messages (pagination)
POST /api/v1/conversations/:id/messages - Send message
PUT /api/v1/conversations/:id/read - Mark as read

Admin (Admin only):
GET /api/v1/admin/users - List users
PUT /api/v1/admin/users/:id/ban - Ban user
GET /api/v1/admin/stats - Basic stats